HEADWORD: Zed
<hw>Zed</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F., probably through It.
<ets>zeta</ets>, fr. L. <ets>zeta</ets>. See <er>Zeta</er>.]</ety>
<def>The letter <er>Z</er>; -- called also <altname>zee</altname>, and
formerly <altname>izzard</altname>.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧<xex>Zed</xex>, thou
unnecessary letter!⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
